⭐ DOCUMENT 7 — Public‑Safe Summary of the System
Title:
What This System Does — A Public‑Safe Overview

Body:
The IP Continuity Watermark Standard and the VaultForge‑Live continuity system provide creators with a simple, public‑safe 
method to:

signal authorship

create timestamped records

strengthen visibility

join a global creator network

build compounding continuity

This system does not replace copyright, legal filings, or professional advice. It provides a public continuity layer that 
supports creators without exposing private data or internal mechanics.

Creators retain full ownership of their work.
Participation is voluntary and free.
